  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        The study will include all patients that met the following criteria:

          1. Diagnosis of schizophrenia according to DSM-IV-TR

          2. Age between 18-65 years

        To obtain the representative results for the prevalence of the MetS in schizophrenic
        patients stratified age and gender, we plan to evaluate about one thousand patients in
        twenty nationwide centers.

          1. 20 centers were selected to provide the representative results of prevalence of the
             MetS

          2. 50 patients in each center were consecutively enrolled
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
